<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
       <h1>About Me</h1>
   
   <div class="row">
     <div class="col-md-5">
     <%= image_tag "Catalina.jpg", width: 350, alt: "Profile image" %> 
     
     <div class="skills">
       <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
       <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
       <div class="progress">
         <div 
         class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
         role="progressbar"
         aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
         aria-valuemax="100"
         style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
         ></div>
         </div>
       <% end %>
      </div>
     </div>
     
     <div class="col-md-7">
       <p>I'm new to programming, but I'm learning quickly and my interest continues to grow. I'm currently learning Ruby on Rails. I also have some experience with HTML and CSS.</p>
     
       <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-info"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#workHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="workHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-info"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="workHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Seven Peaks Waterpark 
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Five Guys Burgers and Fries
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Five Sushi Brothers
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Provo High School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Code to Success Graduate
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
